<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h3 id="head-fed865967efd1f3d680df759d6194f9953a25e0e">The Star of Elendil</h3>
<p>
<em>The shining Star of the West, a famed heirloom of Elendil's house. </em> 
</p>
<p>
It can be activated for light (dam 2d15) &amp; map area every 50+d50 turns if it is being worn. It grants you the power of detect curses if it is being worn. It provides light (radius 4) forever. It increases your speed by 1. It provides resistance to life draining. It allows you to see invisible monsters. It cannot be harmed by acid, cold, lightning or fire.  
</p>
